Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.71,0:00:10.64,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:46.73,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)}The Man Named Fanzell Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:09.70,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fanzell Kruger: the former instructor \Nof the Diamond Kingdom's magic soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:12.86,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,who also happened to be the one who \Ntaught Asta how to use his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:18.11,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You're following up too late \Nwith your left foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:21.82,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to attack consecutively, \Ndon't pause between each slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:23.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:27.58,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Some time had passed since they met,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:30.96,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and Asta was gravely injured in the battle \Nagainst the Diamond Kingdom's assassin,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.33,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Mars, in the dungeon exploration mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:38.88,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle was gathering nourishing herbs \Nthat would help him recover faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:42.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Herbs, herbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:43.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:47.85,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, silver-haired girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.10,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you. You have a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.40,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.75,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:58.18,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to let me see for \Na second. Just a quick second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:02:59.32,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Just a tiny bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.32,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:02.68,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:05.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,...pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:07.84,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I promise I'm not someone suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:09.28,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:12.13,top,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're obviously very suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, what's all that racket?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:14.29,top,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.29,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get any sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.74,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Noe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:17.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,La?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.18,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.68,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:31.52,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a second, miss... \NI'm even willing to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:45.07,main,charmy,0000,0000,0000,,"Pan" and "pants" might sound similar, \Nbut pants aren't edible! La!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:49.12,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You poor girl, running into a pervert like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.15,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:54.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You twisted bastard. What were you \Ntrying to do to my squad member?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:56.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You better be thankful we didn't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.86,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.44,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I was the victim of a robbery, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.18,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,No excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.18,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's fight some more! \NI haven't had enough yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.85,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Before he ever has a chance to \Nappear in front of Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:09.78,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:11.62,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Magic Knights HQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.61,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,This is Finral, the hottie from the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:16.86,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We've apprehended someone suspicious, \Nso we're coming to hand him over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:20.11,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Please, wait! \NHonestly, this is all a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not falling for that.\NI only use bait when I'm fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:25.29,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I don't know much about fishing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:26.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Zell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.66,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:28.74,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:31.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Zell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.17,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:36.45,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,So you were able to join the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.52,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:42.06,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so it was just a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:44.05,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you really were robbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.34,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You should've said so earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.40,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure you guys\N weren't going to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.52,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about the minor details?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.74,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:55.06,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the kind of pan \Nyou can actually eat, la.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:56.56,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.61,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,You're my new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:02.03,top,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know more about you. \NLet's talk into the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.03,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:07.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Zell, was it? Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:10.43,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm pretty sure this is \Nthe first time we've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:13.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you doing here, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:15.10,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.00,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.84,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry for scaring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:22.17,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask you about your wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,My wand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:25.90,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.72,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fairly certain that the wand
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.76,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,you're using was created by \NDomina, who I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:31.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Domina?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:35.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:40.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But the person who gave me \Nthis wand was named Code.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:43.13,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It wasn't Domina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.56,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,So I was right. There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.72,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Her full name is Dominante Code.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:49.66,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:52.66,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The black market in the castle city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.25,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:55.80,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.29,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Old man! That means Domina's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! Hurry up and go see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.57,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.97,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.39,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.41,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:16.46,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, I should be able to reunite \Nwith someone very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.81,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't do that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So, can I go, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but don't blab about us trying \Nto get you arrested by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.69,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You actually just admitted \Nyou made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.06,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:36.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Finral, take them to their \Ndestination with your spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.50,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take a dump and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.04,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.50,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.59,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I stick around too long, \Nit'll make it harder to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.30,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.61,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't for very long, but I'm \Nglad I got to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.95,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again. And make \Nsure you become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:58.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah! And you better \Nlive happily ever after!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.48,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:07.36,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.86,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what? Are we being attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:12.74,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably the assassins \Nwho were after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:15.37,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:20.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is this? Who do I \Nneed to kill for this, and how?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:27.88,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:32.89,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Instructor Fanzell, \NI thought he'd come straight out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:35.31,top,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how things play out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:41.58,sign_10911_127_Diamond_Kingdom_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(760,787)}Diamond Kingdom Assassination Squad Commander\N{\fs30}Galleo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:38.99,top,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Squads 1 through 4,\Nmaintain formation and advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:42.10,top,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Squads 5 and 6, stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:46.41,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Is that building some kind \Nof apartment complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:49.31,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:52.11,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Galleo, could you \Nuse your spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:56.26,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,For insurance, just in case this \Nsurprise attack fails, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.37,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's necessary, but fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:03.67,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be a laughing stock if a \Nplan like this actually failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:09.65,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the glare? Did you\Nforget who let you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.47,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I know I owe you my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.30,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:16.79,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd like to give you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:19.31,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,My instructor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.56,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,is very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.89,italics,Scout,0000,0000,0000,,Scout from Unit 1 reporting.\NWe're within twenty meters of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:30.28,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,All right, prepare to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.37,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,There's the target. Don't let\N him get away. After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:43.91,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Creation Magic: \NThunderbolt Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:48.59,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Prison Death Scattershot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:58.57,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the hell? Our surprise \Nattack actually worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:01.64,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe these guys aren't so strong after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:05.32,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That works for me. Looks like \Nthere are plenty of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.44,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,so let's have them play with us \Nuntil their kneecaps shatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.33,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Squads 1 and 2, continue pursuing the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.00,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:21.78,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to end this quickly \Nso I can go see Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.97,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic: Reflect Refrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.72,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll get things started.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:52.67,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness Magic: Dark Cloaked Lightless Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:03.49,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,None shall ever lay a finger on my food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:10.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go too overboard.\NMake sure you leave some for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:12.17,italics,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,That water barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.77,italics,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't created to stop our attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:18.86,italics,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,but so their own magic \Nwouldn't destroy the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.44,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You the commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.07,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,You're Fanzell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.86,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! You can't lay a finger on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.69,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care what happens to the hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:29.35,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Hostage? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:32.84,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Dominante Code...\N Mariella's heading to her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:37.56,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think we didn't \Nknow where Code was hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.04,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let go of me, or—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:41.44,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the captain's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:43.83,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,To think he was exactly \Nright about what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.41,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.74,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,My teammates are heading out to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:50.20,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Domina via spatial magic as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:52.63,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,They've probably already found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:54.44,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:04.39,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Just how long does it take you to \Ncome get me, you worthless fiancé?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:10.50,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you leave a delicate \Nflower like me alone for so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:17.82,sign_16097_181_MISSING,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(946,1)}Dominante Code
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:17.82,top,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,I... was so worried! I was \Nafraid you were hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.41,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You're kind of hurting me right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:22.38,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.93,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd do this much for me \Njust because I gave you a little extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:31.72,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Bruce was right about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.43,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:35.34,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,And you must be Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How do you—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:40.28,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,You look as gutsy as I've heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:41.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:42.76,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're Mariella!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.33,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:05.32,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,What are you expecting a \Nsingle girl to do, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You and your buddies beat the \Ncrap out of your instructor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:10.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably plotting \Nthe same thing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.87,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I mean no harm, \Nbut please allow me to use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:15.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.46,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:20.50,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you're the Black Bulls...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:23.93,italics,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Did Mariella have us attack \Nwithout knowing who they were?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:29.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You had those guys attack the Black Bulls' \Nbase so we'd take care of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:33.14,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,While that was happening,\N I headed to the black market
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:36.10,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,to tell Miss Domina that \Nthe instructor was coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.31,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,so we were getting prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:41.49,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Though I didn't think you'd get here so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:46.28,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I've drawn out a safe \Nescape route on this map.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.18,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Mariella?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.75,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Including the ones that \Nwere sent to the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:55.97,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to take care of \Nabout sixty assassins at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.59,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, Instructor Fanzell and \NMiss Domina will be able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:03.37,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure these incidents will set \Nthe organization back substantially.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:07.67,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,This is my revenge against the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:09.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:13.81,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Instructor Fanzell... \NI'm tired of this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:19.71,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm also not prepared to be \Non the run for the rest of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.70,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,like Instructor Fanzell and Miss Domina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:24.53,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I decided to exact a huge revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:28.70,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,then present myself to the \NClover Kingdom's Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You just... decided that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:35.04,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for all of \Nthese circumstances to align.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.41,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:40.33,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to see Instructor Fanzell \Nbeing dragged into the Black Bulls' base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:44.05,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if I got you involved, \Nyou'd annihilate the assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:46.39,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Did you, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:48.13,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:52.68,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,So please, capture me. Then this \Nwill end happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:56.27,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think it'll work out that well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:14:02.00,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Considering everything you've done,\N you'll probably be severely punished,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:05.94,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,and you might face retaliation from the \Norganization while you're serving time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:08.25,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,And that's perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:10.95,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be content with accepting \Nanything other than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:19.42,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when you said, "You're supposed \Nto find a reason to live for yourself"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.00,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,It was condescending. \NWho do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:23.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:26.76,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,But your words resonated with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:27.80,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,You were really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.45,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,The punishment I receive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:37.53,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,will be the cost for me to restart \Nand atone for everything I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:41.40,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I believe I need to accept the\N punishment, no matter how severe it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.94,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Mariella...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.32,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:48.12,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Galleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:51.11,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,You're a commander,\Nand you deserted your squads?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.07,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.12,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last person I \Nwant to hear that from!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.88,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be executed so badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:57.62,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll personally do it for you,\N right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.33,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:04.13,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,He might not sound too dangerous, \Nbut his magic is a bit troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:08.30,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Creation Magic: Unopening Red Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.96,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Creation Magic: Crevice Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are these creepy guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And what's this creepy room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:28.87,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,This is a room that Galleo \Ncreated with magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:32.89,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,and those things are magic soldiers \Nthat he can only create in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:36.47,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,They're strong. But more importantly, \Nwhat were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:39.43,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you throw yourself in front of \Na spell without knowing the consequences?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:43.06,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,If that had been an attack spell, \Nyou might be dead right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.21,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:45.75,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.08,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:50.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If it means just letting \Nsomeone die, I'd rather be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:54.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, I'm not \Nthe same person anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:57.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm Asta, a member of the \NMagic Knights squad, the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.20,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I'm your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:00.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:04.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,When there's someone in need, I can help \Nthem out as much as I want, whenever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:12.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you get that, let me \Nsave you while you support me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.20,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be as big-hearted as him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.29,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't just sit back and watch \Nwhen my student's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.03,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together and get through this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:25.04,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Get through this... Can we, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:33.14,main,Galleo,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These two...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights HQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:38.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is Yami from the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:44.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I captured a bunch of troublemakers.\NCould you hurry and come get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:49.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That guy had this many people after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:52.87,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is that Fanzell guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:56.06,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Fanzell? Wasn't his name Zell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:59.58,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Grey said that his real name is Fanzell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:02.91,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He's Fanzell Kruger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:09.02,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He was one of the commanders of \Nthe Diamond Kingdom's armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I met him a long time ago during a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:13.97,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:19.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard he became an instructor for \Nother soldiers, but he must've defected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why all these guys were after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:25.59,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're making this sound \Nlike it's not our problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:32.01,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, does that mean we ended up \Naiding a major enemy's escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:35.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gauche...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.22,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.24,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention this to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:42.74,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell a soul, so please give \Nme a week of Marie vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're only allowed to see her \Nonce a month, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:50.67,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll spend 168 hours of the week staring at\N Marie in such a way that I won't get caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:58.48,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the mysterious incident in \Nwhich the Black Bulls' base got attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:00.92,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.92,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's all right for us to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:13.94,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling we'd be causing you \Ntrouble if we just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:18.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami didn't seem to \Ncare about that, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:20.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Finral?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.70,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:23.43,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it's not fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.75,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I have a really bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:28.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And are you guys sure you \Nwant to take that brat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,with the terrible personality with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:33.52,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't choose to have\N this terrible personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:39.57,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that they were going to try to \Nkidnap me, but she put a stop to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.96,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,And if you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:44.74,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,she's the reason I was able\N to be reunited with Zell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:49.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if you're just too nice, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.80,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you're all pushovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.68,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can trick you all so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:58.82,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I didn't ask you to do all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.61,main,mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't have help \Nfrom you pushovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:03.70,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You can survive on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:06.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you have been?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:11.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually a lot easier to carry \Nall the burden yourself, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:14.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You can just tell yourself that as long as \Nyou can get through it, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't have to think \Nabout everyone around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,so you don't have to think \Nabout anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:23.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not possible anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:26.02,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,When people care for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:28.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,none of your problems are \Njust your own anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:35.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You have to think about them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So I hope you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:41.91,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have a terrible \Npersonality yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:45.08,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want people to think I \Nhave a good personality, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.38,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.32,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we linger too long,\N the goodbyes will be—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop getting all emotional!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Time flows differently for \Nthose who actually try
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,to get stuff done and \Nthose who don't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:02.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So get going, and make Domina happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.77,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:07.43,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I won't waste this precious \Ntime that's been given to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:11.73,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'll do my best \Nto live along with these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:17.74,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write you a letter once \Neverything settles down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:23.66,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh... I hate to ask \Nat a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:27.51,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,But you know how I lost all \Nmy belongings to the assassins
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:30.62,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,right before you guys hauled \Nme off to your hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:37.17,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Could you lend me some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:42.08,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,I never should've saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:47.93,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This was how Fanzell, Domina, \NMariella, and the Black Bulls met.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:52.76,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And currently, Noelle and \NFinral have come to visit Fanzell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:55.85,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,in search of a way to heal Asta's arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.04,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Domina, Mariella, how have you be—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:01.78,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,You worthless husband! Would you fix \Nyour bad habit of getting naked already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.55,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop! That's something I can't control!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:08.53,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,This house is already pretty run-down. \NCould you not mess it up more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:13.85,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So something like \Nthat happened to Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.87,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,He's been through a lot \Nfor someone so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:20.17,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,His streak of bad luck is quite \Nthe contrast to his height.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:25.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any ideas on how to fix \NAsta's arms? Even if it's just a rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.74,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,An ancient curse, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:30.81,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:33.89,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,My home, the Witches' Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The Witches' Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.36,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,With the magic of the queen there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:50.12,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:52.01,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The smartest witch to ever grace this world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:54.37,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,since the creation of the \Nland of witches is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.89,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I need something, so open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:41.94,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We might be able to fix Asta's arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:44.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's infiltrate \Nthe Witches' Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:46.41,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, so many pretty witchies!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.41,0:23:48.41,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna infiltrate that girl's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.41,0:23:51.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 57: "Infiltration."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 57\N\N{\fs18} Infiltration
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:53.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to fill your heart with me!
